snippet.title: ⭐ Super Mario 64 PC Port - Mods - Odyssey Mario's Moveset v7.0.0 - Motos grabs - 4K 60FPS
snippet.description:

https://www.amazon.com/shop/unreal

"Motos (Render96 only):

Motos are rather slow and their jumps ((A)) are low, but nothing can hurt them (except lava) and they can open doors.
Near an object, press (B) to grab it. Once grabbed, Motos can move it with ease. Press (B) again to throw the held object.
More than 50 different objects can be grabbed and throw by a captured Motos!"


Mod exclusively for the Super Mario 64 PC Port, developed by PeachyPeach.

***More info, changelog, build instructions and more in the link below.

Odyssey Mario's Moveset:
https://github.com/PeachyPeachSM64/sm64ex-omm
